IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. GREETER.
DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 RESULT PIC X(30).
01 FIRST PIC X(5) VALUE "Alice".
01 CSV PIC X(20) VALUE "red,green,blue".
01 PART1 PIC X(8).
01 PART2 PIC X(8).
01 PART3 PIC X(8).
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PROC.
    STRING "Hello, " FIRST "!" DELIMITED BY SIZE INTO RESULT.
    DISPLAY RESULT.
    UNSTRING CSV DELIMITED BY "," INTO PART1, PART2, PART3.
    DISPLAY PART1.
    DISPLAY PART2.
    DISPLAY PART3.
    STOP RUN.
